{"tid":1890886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想分享兩單case","createTime":"2020-02-21T12:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T15:01:30.000Z","uid":164590,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3a7d0ee382915aa8b06d168aca4ab5cd28c52d","tid":1890886,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:15:54.000Z","msg":"Anderson v Heatherwood and Wrexham Park Hospitals NHS Trust<br />\n簡單啲來講呢，就係有條友肺炎死咗。佢間醫院俾人告醫療失當，佢告得入因為入院嗰陣如果得到適當同埋快速治療仍然有機會生存而唔會死撚咗<br />\n<br />\n但係呢<br />\n<br />\nJohn Anderson v Milton Keynes General NHS Trust, Oxford Radcliffe Hospital NHS Trust<br />\n<br />\n呢單case條友高唔入因為佢入院嗰陣嗰啲病毒已經入咗骨，就算佢得到適當嘅治療啲病菌好可能會免疫，所以以loss of chance 就高唔入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁即係話<br />\n<br />\n如果有隻新型嘅肺炎，而家都未知有咩療程或者抗體，咁樣 loss of chance 係好可能告唔入㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位醫護，放心去做啦！當然係好好咁治療佢哋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：我唔係讀法律，一啲飯都唔識，淨係咁岩上咸網諗住打飛機見到呢幾個case，是但鳩噏咁樣。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b88a9a44ff356b4d1c776ec4015db7147c7c1556","tid":1890886,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"dcb21bda65661e796c7d511f8a581687f9569218","tid":1890886,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:18:40.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b17b83e076b2113712219ac42f7c33cefdd1c067","tid":1890886,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:20:19.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"f04e96c83b7be6ac6fc7805159d0fddc087ed75f","tid":1890886,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:21:36.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"390df549ad91549b4521b7d0306ef1b8beb434d0","tid":1890886,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T12:23:06.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"a5405da3db0dd51673ed00010d716fd8df6f6f8a","tid":1890886,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":